Mombasa, Kenya: Three Akasha&#39;s sons and fugitive Goswami were charged with affray in a Mombasa court. The court later released on them on Sh20,000 cash bail as police launch hunt for Ali Punjani.Baktash Akasha and Ibrahim Akasha and two foreigners from India and Pakistan have been battling extradition in a Mombasa court since November 2014. The Akashas were indicted in New York alongside Indian felon Vijaygiri Goswami and Gulam Hussein (from Pakistan) with narcotic-related charges and face extradition to the USA.